{"type": "article", "id": 38066, "title": "没有爱琴海的浪漫风格，这间希腊酒店打造的是另一种高级", "description": "尽管同样不便宜", "date": "2017-02-23T23:01:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 667, "name": "酒店"}, {"id": 12175, "name": "希腊"}, {"id": 30668, "name": "爱琴海"}], "category": 17, "author": 699147, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 217, "image": "img/article/article_show/201702221713432hN3aTdtkHXSUF09.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>位于希腊西部小岛 Skiathos 上的 Skiathos Blu Hotel，和爱琴海沿岸的众多酒店有些不同。尽管命名（有蓝色一词）有些随大流，但整间酒店的陈设色调偏暗，白色的墙面也显得很粗粝，似乎无意追随爱琴海白房子的纯净与悠长夏日的阳光感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171422eUhdFJHT48bYgmZ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671211\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>不过，这种与童话、梦幻、浪漫等词汇不沾边的设计，却更真实地呈现出了当地的民俗特色与淳朴民风。</p><p>原木、藤编、草编以及麻料，是频繁出现的几个元素。大堂的设计奠定了整间酒店的基调。几根未经加工的圆木，作为支柱，将铺满浅棕色长木条的天花板和抛光地板连接在了一起。木制元素在宽敞的空间中随处可见。波西米亚风格中不可或缺的藤编和草编制品，做成了灯罩、圆形地毯、水果篮、椅面和各种小装饰物。座椅和长沙发上的坐垫和靠枕，都用麻料制成并装饰上了条纹和小小的几何图案</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171523TNaqcS5xyG4v2lfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664251\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171523E0tAu38p2BNXGfkI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171523h4AWSZa1lxwIB23r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171524TbDfoJP2WqCdHMcN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171524O8IVldysfAt2ZQ9X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750194\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171524MXWrI0KHhwqoOgzG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669558\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171524SN6f0KwDgBclWsdy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>用宽木条拼成的矮桌还挺特别，桌面正中挖出了一个小方块，铺了点泥土，种上了植物。吧台处，还挂了几个圆筒状的草编篓，里面插入了几束干花。几把黑色藤鞭椅的造型，有点像贝壳，又像是渔夫尖尖的帽子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171603aELX2vq9eiDUgYM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171603gmjRrzVEdQIKG8Yu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750192\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这些好玩的细节，也被雅典的室内设计工作室 Stones&amp;Walls 运用到了酒店房间的设计上。粗加工后的圆木桩，被做成了床头柜。灯饰则很多样，有被制成鸟笼状的吊灯，也有可爱的圆形水泥灯。房间内还摆放了一些供人把玩的小物件，比如陶罐和装饰上了草编纹路的木盘。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221716463XrUN2f8iBdleLQn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672797\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171646I39Kn7izA4PcWTGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171646EeYp3TFyuIVah5Kw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688089\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017022217164887tINmZBrDW03iyP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707280\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171647RvClamZsYy4GDg01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221716489c1BK0E2gq65hlDR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750192\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171647eZELum5dt7jlHqN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750392\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221716477tPkzrvbZTc52L0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712654\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171647CryL8HtdJnTQpclA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747227\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这间酒店依山而建。主楼位于顶端，往下是建在斜坡上的几排单层小屋。绕着酒店建筑四处转悠，可以欣赏山景，也能眺望到爱琴海。从酒店往山下走 300 多级台阶，就能到达海滩。</p><p>酒店所在的小岛 Skiathos （斯基亚索斯），名声不如圣托里尼等岛屿那么响亮，不过全岛共有 60 多处海滩，还有成片的松林。岛上的斯基亚索斯镇有铺满鹅卵石的窄窄街道，以及四间古老的教堂。每年七八月，不少欧洲人都会选择来这里度假。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702221717553EztRr8cwqOJ5skM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">斯基亚索斯的海滩（来源：<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skiathos\" rel=\"nofollow\">wikipedia</a>）</figcaption></figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.skiathosblu.gr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Skiathos Blu Hotel</a> 的售价每人每晚的最少花费约为 700 人民币。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171949yQLzxKU4AHmnuiJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761106\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171949yapBV0kFNtTUWnZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171951U8HCZXVOdjGuxJyP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679724\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170222171951ihs54qCozxepIcR8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692177\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图及文内图（如无注明）均来自&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.skiathosblu.gr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Skiathos Blu Hotel</a></p>"}